- How are you doing?

1035
00:53:36,167 --> 00:53:41,041
Oh, I'm--I'm good.

1036
00:53:41,042 --> 00:53:46,874
I think I'm finally getting
a handle on all this mess.

1037
00:53:46,875 --> 00:53:48,333
Well, that's great.

1038
00:53:51,292 --> 00:53:53,916
