1077
00:58:38,292 --> 00:58:40,625
You and Betsy
are still coming, right?

1078
00:58:42,833 --> 00:58:46,625
I'm sorry,
but Betsy's in heaven now.

1079
00:58:50,958 --> 00:58:53,125
My girl is finally out
of her pain.

1080
00:58:54,208 --> 00:58:55,667
That--

1081
00:59:21,417 --> 00:59:24,541
